102
00:06:42,409 --> 00:06:42,970
Yu Chen!

103
00:06:43,650 --> 00:06:44,260
Master.

104
00:06:47,940 --> 00:06:49,200
What's this all about?

105
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:51,650
It's damp and cold on the mountain at night.

106
00:06:51,650 --> 00:06:52,500
I made a quilt for you, Master,

107
00:06:52,500 --> 00:06:53,770
to keep you warm.

108
00:06:54,290 --> 00:06:55,409
Back in the village,

109
00:06:55,409 --> 00:06:56,090
I often helped people

110
00:06:56,090 --> 00:06:57,290
with sewing and mending.

111
00:06:57,290 --> 00:06:58,550
