114
00:07:01,430 --> 00:07:02,380
I didn't bring you here

115
00:07:02,380 --> 00:07:03,710
to do chores for others.

116
00:07:04,580 --> 00:07:05,500
I just wanted to

117
00:07:05,500 --> 00:07:07,100
repay you properly, Master.

118
00:07:08,020 --> 00:07:08,940
I embroidered

119
00:07:09,450 --> 00:07:10,830
these flowers

120
