121
00:07:21,290 --> 00:07:22,350
Where are my books?

122
00:07:23,890 --> 00:07:24,890
I found those old books

123
00:07:24,890 --> 00:07:25,850
all damp and wet,

124
00:07:26,020 --> 00:07:28,150
so I took them outside to dry in the sun.

125
00:07:28,260 --> 00:07:29,120
You dried them?

126
00:07:39,650 --> 00:07:40,710
What's happening?

127
00:07:40,940 --> 00:07:43,140
Why are these characters fleeing away?

128
00:07:44,180 --> 00:07:45,060
The immortal's secret texts

129
00:07:45,060 --> 00:07:46,820
