133
00:07:51,670 --> 00:07:53,400
You're the first one to do this.

134
00:07:53,770 --> 00:07:54,970
What should we do now?

135
00:07:56,210 --> 00:07:57,409
There's only one way.

136
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:58,380
Put these characters

137
00:07:58,380 --> 00:07:59,350
